title: 9CD length Sampler
description:
This is a large selection of great music from relatively unknown to obscure artists that is approximately 9CD in length. Although there are a few much better known artists, I have tried to include lesser known tracks. 

This is an extended version of a previous torrent I had that was called '5 CD length sampler' or something like that. This current upload has many more tracks that the original one did not. I tried to include a text file giving details of the individual tracks, but it would not upload here with the FLAC files . So I have made a separate torrent that you should be able to find if you search other uploads I have done.  


This collection really has some fantastic music that should give hours of entertainment and introduce most of you to some tremendous little known artists. 

Good luck, and please seed!
